## Introduction
Handle Form data and Validation with ease.

## Install
run `composer require gufran/former *` or add this to your `composer.json` file

    "require": {
        "gufran/former": "*"
    }

and run `composer install`

## Documentation
Refer to the [Documentation](http://www.gufran.me/post/handle-form-data-and-validation) post on my blog.

